<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;; font-size:xx-small;">This box: <a href="/wiki/Template:Computer_security" title="Template:Computer security"><span title="View this template" style="">view</span></a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Computer_security" title="Template talk:Computer security"><span title="Discussion about this template" style="">talk</span></a></div>
